Author: mij3i
Text: I'm currently doing IOP after doing inpatient, residential, and php a bunch of times. I'm seeing my therapist in a few days so hopefully that helps. . . It just sucks because I feel like I can't give myself permission to eat unless I'm in one of those higher levels of care (residential or inpatient) idk maybe this means I'm not really ready to be out of treatment? Idk :/

Author: helpwitheating
Text: Would you consider therapy? Sometimes you need professional help to give yourself permission to eat - I did. Helps a lot.
